

 Full Premium Employee Panel
A professional-grade, interactive dashboard built for modern business management. This panel allows employees to track project milestones, manage financial invoices, and communicate with administrators and clients in real-time.
 Project Milestones: What we have done till now
We have successfully built the core infrastructure of the platform. Key achievements include:
Development Environment Setup:
Installed and configured Node.js (v20.11.1) and Vite for high-speed performance.
Initialized Tailwind CSS for modern, utility-first styling.
Architecture & Structure:
Designed a clean, industry-standard folder structure: src/components, src/pages, and src/services.
Optimized index.html routing by positioning it in the project root.
Core Feature Development:
Dashboard Navigation: Integrated react-router-dom for seamless transitions between pages without reloading.
Task Management: Built an interactive Tasks page where employees can toggle statuses between "Pending" and "Completed."
Financial Tracker: Created a sleek Invoice view with custom status badges.
Communication Center: Developed a functional Chat UI using React state for instant messaging simulation.
UI/UX Polishing:
Integrated Lucide-React for premium, sharp iconography.
Fully responsive design using a sophisticated Slate and Indigo color palette.